have the right to wield a sword.

281
00:20:07,290 --> 00:20:08,310
Committed?

282
00:20:09,130 --> 00:20:11,060
Committed to keep carrying on.

283
00:20:27,510 --> 00:20:28,470
Akame!

284
00:20:29,920 --> 00:20:31,530
