imagine on your shoulders,

290
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:52,810
this whole time.

291
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:55,910
Akame,

292
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:59,480
we're done losing things that are precious to us.

293
00:21:27,340 --> 00:21:29,780
What impressive determination.

294
00:21:29,780 --> 00:21:32,470
Your wisdom is a testament to your greatness.

295
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:38,480
